var r=false
function check() {
var x = document.querySelectorAll("input[type='checkbox']")
var y=0
if(!r){
for(var i=0; i<x.length; i++) {
if(x[i].checked!=true) {
x[i].checked=true
}
}}else {
for(var i=0; i<x.length; i++) {
if(x[i].checked!=false) {
x[i].checked=false
}
}
}
if(localStorage["checked"]==x.length) {
r=true
} else {
r=false
}
for(var i=0; i<x.length; i++) {
if(x[i].checked) {
y++
}
}
localStorage['checked']=y

}
